# linux-server-automation

Project structure:
basic/
  - create_users.sh
  - set_permissions.sh
  - install_packages.sh
  - system_info.sh

intermediate/
  - automate_backup.sh
  - log_cleanup.sh
  - check_service_status.sh
  - performance_monitor.sh

All scripts are small, intended as starting points. Make executable and run as root where required.
